\id 1TI Meitei: Roman Script 1st Translation 
\h 1 Timothy 
\toc1 TIMOTHY-DA I-ba Paul-gi Ahanba Chithi 
\toc2 1 Timothy 
\toc3 1 Tim 
\mt1 TIMOTHY-DA 
\mt2 I-ba Paul-gi Ahanba Chithi 
\imt1 Wahoudok 
\ip 1 Timothy hairiba lairik asi Pakhonchatpa Paul-na mahakki tung-inba Timothy-da i-ba chithini. 1 Timothy asi chaorakna Christtana poklaba matung chahi 62-64 aduwaida iramba yai. Masi Paul-gi punsi loiramdai aduwaida oigani. Paul-ga Timothy-ga naknaba mari leirammi, mahakna Timothy-bu ichanupa haina kayarak palli (Philippians 2:22; 1 Timothy 1:2, 1:18). 
\ip Chithi asi Paul-na singlupta nattaduna misak amada i-ba chithi marigi manungda amani. Atoppa chithi ahumdudi 2 Timothy, Titus amasung Philemon-ni. 1 Timothy asi singlupta Tengban Mapu khurumbagi (2:1-15), singlupki ahal ama oibagi magunsing (3:1-13) amasung aranba tambibasinggi maramda piba cheksin wasing (1:3-11, 4:1-5, 6:2-5) hairibasing asigi maramda piba paotak kaya yaori. Timothy-bu singlupsinggi manungda luchingba ama oinaba Paul-na tambiba adu utli. Eikhoigi matam asigi lam lamda leiba singlupsingda karamna yengsin-gadage haibagi singlupki luchingbasingda kanagadaba achumba kaya ama yaori. 
\iot Yaopham Takpa 
\io1 1. Paul-na Timothy-bu khurumjaduna houba \ior (1:1-2)\ior* 
\io1 2. Mahakna Timothy-da aranba tambibasinggi maramda cheksin wa haiba \ior (1:3-11)\ior* 
\io1 3. Jisu Christtagi maramda Paul-na kaya haraojaba haibadu makha tana sandokna takpa \ior (1:12-19)\ior* 
\io1 4. Mathangda mahakna singlupta Tengban Mapu khurumbagi amadi singlupki luchingba ama oibagi maramda Timothy-da paotak piba \ior (2–3)\ior* 
\io1 Timothy-da aroiba paotak piraga Paul-na mahakki chithi asi loisilli \ior (4–6)\ior* 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Eikhoigi Kanbiba Mapu Tengban Mapu Ibungo amasung eikhoigi asa oiriba Christta Jisugi yangthang matung inna Christta Jisugi pakhonchatpa oiriba Paul eihakna-- 
\p  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Pakhon 16:1\x*Thajabagi marida tasengba ichanupa oiriba Timothy-da chithi asi i-jari: 
\p Ipa Ibungo Tengban Mapu amasung eikhoigi Mapu Ibungo Christta Jisuna thoujal, chanbiba amasung ingthaba nangonda pibiba oirasanu. 
\s1 Aranba tambibasinggi maiyokta piba cheksin wa 
\p  
\v 3 Eina Macedonia chatlamdaida eina nangonda kanna haikhibagumna, nahakna Ephesus-ta makha tana leithaba adu eihakna pammi maramdi mapham aduda mi kharana aranba tambiba kaya ama tambiri makhoising adu nahakna lepnanaba yathang pigadabani.  
\v 4 Marei yetnaba khakta thok-hanba thainagi semjin sajinba warising amadi pari purigi sangkhraba mathang mathang chattharakliba parengsing aduda pukning luptanaba makhoida haiyu; madusing aduna thajabagi mapanna khangba Tengban Mapu mahakki thourang aduda kari amata mateng oide.  
\v 5 Yathang asigi pandamdi asengba thammoi, aphaba achum aran khangba pukning amasung tousinnaba yaodaba thajabadagi thorakpa nungsiba aduni.  
\v 6 Mi kharadi masising asidagi leithokkhraga, karisu kanadaba waremda onsin-khre.  
\v 7 Makhoina Tengban Mapugi wayel yathang tambiba oja amadi oining-i, adubu makhoi masana ngangliba wa adu karino haiba makhoina khangjade aduga makhoina yamna thajana ngangliba hiramsing adugi maramda khangjade. 
\p  
\v 8 Wayel Yathang haibasi magi sijinnapham adu chumna sijinnarabadi madu aphabani haiba eikhoina khang-i.  
\v 9 Wayel yathang asi achumba chatpa misinggidamakta semba natte adubu wayel yathang indaba, irang houba mi, Tengban Mapu ningdaba, pap chenba, sengdaba amadi lainingchettaba, makhoigi mama mapabu hatpasing, mihatpasing  
\v 10 nupa nupigi oiba marida lamchat naidaba, nupa masel nupi masel haktinnaba, mi phaduna mibu minai oina lallonbasing, minamba ngangba amadi lanna sakhi pibasing, amasung tambiriba achumbasing adugi onna-teinaba touba makhoi pumnamaksing adugidamak sembani haiba eikhoina khang-i.  
\v 11 Tambiriba achumbasing adu eibu sandoknaba sinnabiriba aphaba pao aduda yao-i, Aphaba Pao adudi yaipharaba matik mangalgi Tengban Mapudagi lakpani. 
\s1 Tengban Mapugi thoujal-gidamak thagatchaba 
\p  
\v 12 Eibu panggal pibiriba eikhoigi Mapu Ibungo Christta Jisubu eina thagatchei, madudi Ibungo mahakki thougalgidamak mahakna eibu khandokpiduna eibu thajaba yaba oina singthabire.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Pakhon 8:3; 9:4,5\x*Houkhiba matam amada eihak Ibungobu thina ngangba, ot-neiba amasung Ibungobu ikaiba piba oiramlabasu madu eina toukhiba adu khangdabadagi amadi thajaba leitribagi oiba maramna eibu Tengban Mapuna chanbiba utpire.  
\v 14 Eikhoigi Mapu Ibungogi thoujal adu eingonda marang kaina heithabire aduga Christta Jisuda leiba thajaba amasung nungsiba aduga loinana eingonda pibire.  
\v 15 Christta Jisuna pap chenbasingbu kanbinaba taibangpan asida lengbirakpani haiba wapham asi thajaba yaba amadi mapung phana lousinbada matik chabani. Pap chenbasinggi marakta eihakna khwaidagi henna pap chenbani.  
\v 16 Adum oinamak maram asigidamak haibadi pap chenbasinggi marakta khwaidagi pap chenba eingonda Tengban Mapuna chanbiba adu utpire, madu Ibungo mahakpu tungda thajagababa amadi lomba naidaba punsi phanggadaba mi pumnamakta Christta Jisuna mahakki kuina khaangheiba adu pandam oina utpinanabani.  
\v 17 Lomba naidaba Ningthou, siba naidraba, uba ngamdaba, amatta ngairaba Tengban Mapu Ibungo mangonda matam pumnamakta ikai khumnaba amasung matik mangal leiba oirasanu! Amen. 
\p  
\v 18 Eigi ichanupa Timothy, nahakki maramda Tengban Mapugi wa phongdokkhiba adugi matung inna yathang asi eina nangonda piri, madusing adu ningsingduna ningthijana lan soknou,  
\v 19 thajaba amasung amakpa leitaba achum aran khangba pukning adu chetna paiyu. Mi kharanadi makhoigi achum aran khangba pukning adu thawoidabadagi, makhoigi thajaba adu pummang manghalle.  
\v 20 Makhoidugi marakta Hymenaeus amasung Alexander-su yao-i, makhoina Tengban Mapubu thina ngangba adu toknaba eina makhoibu Satan-gi makhutta sinnare. 
\c 2  
\s1 Singlupta Tengban Mapu khurumbagi maramda takpi tambiba 
\p  
\v 1-2 Eikhoina Tengban Mapuda laining chetna amadi asengba punsi mahing amaga loinana ingna chikna panba punsi ama hingba yananaba mi pumnamakki, ningthousinggi amasung angam athou pumnamakkidamak wakatpiba, nibiba, haijabiba amasung thagatnaba eina ahanbamaktada nahakpu thougatli.  
\v 3 Eikhoigi Kanbiba Mapu Tengban Mapu Ibungogi maphamda masi aphaba amasung apenbani,  
\v 4 mi pumnamakna kanbiba phangba amasung makhoina achumba adubu khangba haibasi Ibungo mahakna pammi.  
\v 5 Maramdi Tengban Mapu ama lei aduga Tengban Mapu amasung mioibabu tainabiba misak ama lei, mahak adudi mioiba ama oiriba Christta Jisuni.  
\v 6 Mahakna mioiba pumnamakpu thadokpinaba thadokmal oina mahak masamakpu pibire. Achaba matamda mi pumnamakpu kanbiba Tengban Mapuna pammi haibasi masina pramanni,  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt 2 Tim 1:11\x*maram asigidamak Jihudi nattabasingda pakhonchatpa amadi tambiba ama oina thajaba amadi achumbagi paojel sandoknaba eibu thabire. Eihakna chinthiba natte; achumba adu hairibani! 
\p  
\v 8 Aduna Tengban Mapu khurumbagi thouram khudingda asaoba amasung yetnaba yaodana Tengban Mapugidamak katthoklaba nupasingna khut thanggattuna Tengban Mapuda haijaba adu eina pammi.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt 1 Pet 3:3\x*Nupisingna ing tappa amasung mapham matam khangbaga loinana ningthijana phijet setpa asisu eina pammi; ahenba leitengna sambu make semba nattraga sanana nattraga mani-muktana nattraga mamal yamba phijetna leitengdasanu,  
\v 10 adubu Tengban Mapu ningbi nupi ama oibagi matik chaba aphaba thabaksingna leitengsanu.  
\v 11 Nupisingna tuminna leiduna amadi nolukpaga loinana tamjasanu.  
\v 12 Nupina tambiba, nattraga nupagi mathakta panba eina yade, makhoi tuminna leigadabani.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Meihou 2:7; Meihou 2:21,22\x*Maramdi Adam-bu hanna sembikhibani aduga mathangda Eve-pu sembibani.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Meihou 3:1-6\x*Namthak toukhiba adu Adam-bu natte; nupi adubu namthak touduna Tengban Mapugi wayel yathang thugaikhibani.  
\v 15 Adubu nupisingna\f + \fr 2:15 \ft Greek-tadi “mahak” haibani\f* thajabada, nungsibada, asengbada amasung phajaba lamchatta leirabadi, chabokpagi mapanna makhoibu kanbigani. 
\c 3  
\s1 Singlupki luchingbasinggi maramda haiba 
\p  
\v 1 Wapham asi achumbani: Kanagumba mi amana singlup amagi luchingba ama oiba pamlabadi, mahakna aphaba thabak amabu pamlabani.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2-7 \xt Tit 1:6-9\x*Singlupki luchingba ama haibasi mingchat thiningai oiba amakpa leitaba mi, mahakki nupida thajaba yaba oiba, ka hendaba, masa khudum chanjaba, ikai khumnabada matik chaba, lamlanbasingbu mayumda taramna okpa amadi tambiba ngamba mi ama oigadabani;  
\v 3 mahak yuda luppa amadi tamthiba mi ama oiroidabani, adubu pukning tappa, khatnagandaba amadi sel pamgandaba mi ama oigadabani.  
\v 4 Mahakki imung manungbu ningthina yengsinba ama oigadabani aduga mahakki angangsingna mahakpu ikaikhumnabaga loinana mahakna haiba inba haibadu oihan-gadabani.  
\v 5 Maramdi kanagumbana masamakki imung manungbu karamna yengsin-gani haiba khangdrabadi mahakna karamna Tengban Mapugi singluppu ngak-sen-gadage?  
\v 6 Mahak nouna thajarakpa mi ama oiroidabani, nattrabadi mahakna napan touduna chaothoklaklabadi Devil-da takhiba wayel adumak mahaksu taba yai.  
\v 7 Singlupki mi nattabasingna ikaikhumnaba misak ama oigadabani madu oirabadi mahak ikaiba nangduna Devil-gi langda taba haibadu oiraroi. 
\s1 Singlupki thougal toubasing 
\p  
\v 8 Adugumduna, singlupki thougal toubasingsu\f + \fr 3:8 \ft Deacon\f* aphaba lichat chatpa amadi pukchel sengba mi oigadabani; makhoi yuda luppa nattraga selda karamba mi oiroidabani;  
\v 9 asengba achum aran khangba pukningga loinana phongdokpiraba thajabagi oiba achumba adubu makhoina chetna paiba oigadabani.  
\v 10 Ahanbada makhoibu chang yenggadabani, maduda makhoina mai paklabadi makhoina singlupki thougal tousanu.  
\v 11 Makhoigi nupisingsu\f + \fr 3:11 \ft Nattraga Deacon oiba nupi\f* adugumna aphaba lamchat chatpa amadi miwa ngangdaba oigadabani; ka hendaba amadi maram khudingda thajaba yabi oigadabani.  
\v 12 Thougal toubasing adu nupi amakhaktagi mapuroiba oiba, machasing amasung imung manungbu ningthijana yengsinba ngamba mi oigadabani.  
\v 13 Ningthina thougal toubasing aduna makhoi masagidamak aphaba mingchat phangjaduna Christta Jisuda leiba makhoigi thajaba adugi maramda thouna phana ngangba ngammi. 
\s1 Yamna maru oiba athuppa wa 
\p  
\v 14 Eina nahakki nanakta yamna thuna lakkani haiba asa tourabasu, eina nangonda waphamsing asi iri.  
\v 15 Adubu karigumba eihak thengtharaklabadi, Tengban Mapugi imung manung haibadi achumbagi yumbi amadi ngaklou oiriba ahingba Tengban Mapugi singlupta karamba machat chatkadage haibadu chithi asina nangonda khanghan-gani.  
\v 16 Eikhoigi laininggi athuppa asi kayada chaokhrabano haiba asi kana amatana yadaba ngamloi: 
\q1 Ibungo mahak asi mioiba amagi saktamda phongdokpire, 
\q2 Thawai\f + \fr 3:16 \ft thawaigi oiba saktamda achumba oina utpire\f* aduna achumbani haiba utpire, 
\q2 swargadutsingnasu ujare. 
\q1 Ibungo mahakpu phurupsinggi marakta sandokle, 
\q2 taibangpan-gi mapham pumnamakta thajare, 
\q2 amasung swargada loukhatpikhre. 
\c 4  
\s1 Aranba tambibasing 
\p  
\v 1 Akonba matamda mioi kharana thajaba asi thadoktuna, minamba thawaising amadi lai phattabasingna tambibasing adu in-gani haina Thawai Asengbana sengna haibire.  
\v 2 Asigumba tambibasing asi achum aran khangba pukning adu mei ikpa yotna chakkhrabagumna aphasasinnaba minamba ngangbasingna sandok-i.  
\v 3 Makhoina luhongba amadi akaknaba chinjak khara chaba thing-i. Adubu chinjaksingdudi achumba adu khanglaba amadi thajabasingna Tengban Mapubu thagatcharaga chananaba Tengban Mapuna sembikhraba chinjaksingni.  
\v 4 Tengban Mapuna sembikhraba pot khudingmak aphaba ngaktani; thagatpaga loinana lousinjarabadi yadada karisu leite,  
\v 5 maramdi madu Tengban Mapugi wa amadi haijabagi mapanna senghanbire. 
\s1 Christta Jisugi aphaba thougal touba 
\p  
\v 6 Nahakna thajaba nachin nanaosingda hiramsing asi haibirabadi, thajabagi wa amadi nahakna illiba achumba tambiba aduda nahakki thawaigi oiba punsi adu yokkhatchabaga loinana Christtagi aphaba thougal touba mi ama oigani,  
\v 7 Lirubagi karisu kannadaba aduga laininggi maiyokta leiba semjin sajinba warising adudagi namai leithok-u. Tengban Mapu ningba punsi ama hingnabagidamak nasabu sajel toujou.  
\v 8 Hakchang sajel toubagi kannaba khara makhei lei, adubu thawaigi oiba sajeldi hiram khudingmakta kannei, maramdi maduda houjik hinglingei punsi asigidamak amasung lakkadaba punsi adugidamak wasakpiba lei.  
\v 9 Wapham asi achumbani amasung lousinbada matik chabamakni.  
\v 10 Mi pumnamakkidamak, thoidok hendokna thajabasinggidamak Kanbiba Mapu oiriba ahingba Tengban Mapu aduda eikhoigi asa thamjaduna eikhoina thabak nomduna kanna hotnabani. 
\p  
\v 11 Waramsing asi yathang piduna tambiyu.  
\v 12 Kana amatana nahakpu naha oiri haiduna hanthana yenghan-ganu adubu ngangbada, lichat sajatta, nungsibada, thajabada amasung sengna hingba punsida thajabasinggidamak pandam oiyu.  
\v 13 Eina laktriba phaoba nakhoigi tinnabada Tengban Mapugi wahei paba, pao sandokpa amasung tambibada pukning chang-u.  
\v 14 Ahallupna nanggi nathakta khut thambiba matamda Tengban Mapugi wa phongdokpasingna haibikhiba adugi mapanna nangonda pibikhiba thawaigi oiba khudol adu miraiba touganu.  
\v 15 Hairibasing asi thabak oina touduna nasamak katthokchou madu oirabadi mi khudingna nahak chaokhatlakli haibadu ugani.  
\v 16 Nahak nasamakki maramda amadi tambiba adugi maramda cheksillu. Madu touduna leiyu maramdi nahakna madu tourabadi nahak nasamak amadi nahakki wa tabasing adubu kanbigani. 
\c 5  
\s1 Thajabasinggi maphamda tougadaba thoudangsing 
\p  
\v 1 Ahal oirabasingbu thina cheiganu, adubu nahakki ipagumna khanduna pukning thougatpiyu; naha oibasingbu nanaogumna,  
\v 2 ahal oirabi nupisingbu nahakki imagumna amasung naha oibi nupisingna nachan-gumna khanduna pukning sengna loinabiyu. 
\p  
\v 3 Kana leijadrabi lukhrabisingbu ikaikhumnabiyu.  
\v 4 Kanagumbi lukhrabi amagi macha masu leirabadi, macha masusing aduna makhoina ahanbada makhoi masagi imung manungda makhoigi laininggi oiba thoudang adu pangthokpa tamsanu aduga asumna makhoigi mama mapa amadi mapu mabenda laman singsanu maramdi masi Tengban Mapugi maphamda apenbani.  
\v 5 Yengsinbinaba kana leijadrabi lukhrabi aduna Tengban Mapuda asa thamjaduna, mahakpu pangbinaba ahing nungthil animakta haijei.  
\v 6 Adubu masa nungainaba hinglibi lukhrabi adudi hinglabasu mahak sirabani.  
\v 7 Mingchat thiba leitanaba makhoida hiramsing asi haibiyu.  
\v 8 Adubu kanagumbana mahakki mari mata maru oina mahak masamakki imung manunggi mibu yok-thaktrabadi, thajaba asi yajadre amasung thajadaba midagi mahakna henna phattre. 
\p  
\v 9 Chahi humphu sudribi kana amata lukhrabisinggi marakta masing chalhan-ganu. Madugi mathakta mahakki mapuroibagi maphamda thajaba yaba punsi ama hinglambi misak ama oigadabani,  
\v 10 amadi aphaba thabakkidamak mayamna sonnarabi haibadi machasingbu ningthina yok-thaklakpi, lamlanbasingbu taram taram tourambi, Mapu Ibungogi misinggi makhongbu hamdokpirambi, awa ana tarabasingbu pangbirabi amasung aphaba thabak khudingmakta maram okpi oirambi ama oigadabani. 
\p  
\v 11 Naha oiribi lukhrabisingbu lukhrabigi masingda chalhan-ganu, maramdi makhoigi hakchanggi apambana makhoina Christtagidamak katthokchaba adudagi hen-gatlakpada makhoi mayum panninggani.  
\v 12 Asumna makhoigi hanna thamkhiba wasak adu thugaibagi wayel phangba oigani.  
\v 13 Aduta nattana, yum yumda koichat chattuna matam manghanbagi heinabi leigani. Aduga makhoina karisu toudaba aduta nattana warem ngangba amasung migi thabakta khut thingjinduna, makhoina ngangloidaba wa ngangba oigani.  
\v 14 Maram aduna naha oiribi lukhrabisingna amuk hanna mayum panduna machasing poktuna mayum makei ningthina panba haibasi eina pammi. Madu oirabadi yeknabasingna maral sinnabagi khudongchaba adu phanglaroi.  
\v 15 Lukhrabi kharadi leithoktuna Satan-gi matung inkhre.  
\v 16 Kanagumbi thajabi nupi amagi imungda lukhrabising leirabadi, mahakna makhoibu yengsinbigadabani maduna singlupta potlum oihalloidabani, madu oirabadi kana leijadrabi lukhrabisingbu singlupna pangbiba ngamgani. 
\p  
\v 17 Singlupki thabak touduna chingbiriba ahal lamansing, maru oina Tengban Mapugi wahei sandokliba amadi tambiriba makhoising adu saruk ani henna ikai khumnabada matik chai.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 5:18 \xt Aniwa 25:4; Mat 10:10; Luk 10:7\x*Maramdi Mapugi asengba Puyana hai, “Sallababu maheimarong netthat-hallingeida machin pun-ganu” aduga “Thabak suba mina asuman phangba matik chai.”  
\v 19 \x - \xo 5:19 \xt Aniwa 17:6; 19:15\x*Mi ani nattraga ahumgi sakhi leitrabadi, singlupki ahal amagi mathakta maral siba wa louganu.  
\v 20 Mi ateinasu kinaba pap touriba ahansingdu miyam mangda cheiyu. 
\p  
\v 21 Tengban Mapu, Christta Jisu amasung khanggatlaba swargadutsinggi mamangda eina nangonda hairi madudi nahakna achan mirai naidana, misak mimai yengdana hiramsing asi ngak-u.  
\v 22 Tengban Mapugi thougan-gidamak misingbu katthoknaba makhoigi mathakta khut thambada hathu hathuganu. Mi ateigi papka saruk yaminnaganu; nahak nasamak sengna thamjou. 
\p  
\v 23 Nahakna ising khakta thakkanu, nahakki chakkhaogidamak amasung nahakna toina nabagi maramana yu khara khara sijinnou. 
\p  
\v 24 Mi kharagi papti iphong phong-i, wayenbagi maphamda makhoigi mang thana chatli aduga kanagumba kharagi papti makhoigi matung illi.  
\v 25 Adugumduna aphaba thabakti iphon phong-i, aduga iphong phongba nattabasing adusu matam pumbagi oina lottuna thamba ngamde. 
\c 6  
\p  
\v 1 Tengban Mapugi ming amadi eikhoigi tambiba asi thina ngangdanaba, minaigi potpu puribasingna, makhoigi mapusingbu ikai khumnabada matik chabani haina khan-gadabani.  
\v 2 Christian-singna mapu oiriba makhoising aduna, makhoi thajaba maselni haiduna thawoi usittaba touroidabani. Madugi mahutta maduna henna phajana thougal tougadabani; maramdi makhoina touriba thougal adudagi kanaba phangliba adu thajabasingni amasung makhoina nungsijabasingni. 
\s1 Aranba Tambiba amadi Achumba Lan 
\p Hiramsing asi nahakna tambiyu amasung thoujinbiyu.  
\v 3 Eikhoigi Mapu Ibungo Jisu Christtagi achumba wahei amasung eikhoigi laininggi tambiba adudagi tonganba kanagumbana tambirabadi,  
\v 4 makhoidi karisu khangdaba amasung napan toubasingni. Yetnaba amasung waheigi maramda chinda paodanaba pammi maduna kalakpa, yetnaba, yengthinabagi wari, phattana chingnaba thok-halli,  
\v 5 amasung achumba adu leitraba, pukning phattraba misinggi marakta tattana yanadaba thok-halli. Tengban Mapu ningba asi lan-thum tongjanabagi pambeini haina makhoina khalli. 
\p  
\v 6 Adubu penthokpaga loinana Tengban Mapu ningba haibasi yamna tongjabani.  
\v 7 Maramdi eikhoina taibangpanda karisu pudana lakle, aduga masidagi eikhoina karisu puba ngamloi.  
\v 8 Chanaba amasung setnaba leirabadi maduna eikhoi penthokchagani.  
\v 9 Inak khuningba misingdi athembada tai amasung apangba amadi misingbu mangtakpada tahanba phattaba apambasing adugi langda thui.  
\v 10 Sel pamganbadi phattaba pumnamakki hourakphamni; mi kharadi sel pammanbadagi thajabadagi lammuknakhre aduga awaba kayaga loinana makhoigi thamoi kaire. 
\s1 Timothy-da piba aroiba yathang 
\p  
\v 11 Adubu he Tengban Mapugi mi, nahakti pumnamak asidagi chenthok-u. Achumba chatpa, Tengban Mapu ningba, thajaba, nungsiba, khaangheiba, pukning tappa oinanaba hotnou.  
\v 12 Thajabagi akanba laan adu soknou. Lomba naidaba hingba adu chetna paiyu masida nahakpu koubire amasung sakhi kayagi mamangda nahakna phongdokle.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 6:13 \xt Jn 18:37\x*Pumnamakpu hingba pibiriba Tengban Mapu amasung Pontius Pilate-ki mangda mahakki thajaba adu chingnaba leitana haidokkhiba Christta Jisugi mamangda eina nangonda yathang piri,  
\v 14 madudi Ibungo Jisu Christta phongdoktriba phaoba amakpa amasung mingchat thiba yaodana yathang asi ngak-u.  
\v 15 Yaiphaba amasung Leingakpa, ningthousinggi Ningthou amasung mapusinggi Mapu, Tengban Mapuna madu achaba matamda thok-hanbigani.  
\v 16 Sinaidaba asi Ibungo Mahak khaktani amadi kananasu changsinba ngamdaba mangal aduda Ibungo mahak lei. Aduga kana amatana Ibungo mahakpu ukhidri amasung ubasu ngamde. Ibungo mangonda ikai khumnaba amasung lomba naidana panggal leiba oirasanu! Amen. 
\p  
\v 17 Houjikki taibangpanba asida inakkhullibasing makhoina pukning nawangdanaba amadi areppa leitaba landa asa thamdanaba adubu eikhoibu nungainanaba pot pumnamak marang kaina pibiba Tengban Mapuda makhoigi asa thamjanaba yangthang piyu.  
\v 18 Aphaba thabak tounaba, aphaba thabakta inak khunnaba amasung pina heiba oinanaba amadi makhoigi areiba adu ateisingga saruk yaminnanaba makhoida yathang piyu.  
\v 19 Matou asumna lakkadaba matamgidamak makhoina achetpa yumpham thonbagumna makhoigidamak makhoina lansing peisinjagani, asumna achumba hingba oiriba hingba adubu makhoina paijagani. 
\p  
\v 20 Timothy, nangonda sinnaraba adu ngak-u; Tengban Mapubu ikai khumnadaba wa ngangba amadi mioi kharana lanna “Lousingni” haina kounaba yanadaba wakhallonsing adudagi mai leithok-u.  
\v 21 Mioi kharadi madu phangle haijaduna thajaba adudagi leithokkhre. 
\p Thoujalna nakhoi pumnamakta loinabisanu.